The paper deals with scene classification using deep learning techniques and natural language processing methods, which are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) research. The focus is on indoor environments for robots (cs.RO), which is a specific application of computer vision. The paper also discusses the use of word embeddings, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
